      "description": "Four-loop HQET integral topology 4 for the matter-dependent cusp anomalous dimension at small angle. Defined via 16 propagators $D_k$ with $G(a_1,...,a_{16}) = e^{4 \\varepsilon \\gamma_E} \\int \\prod D_k^{-a_k}$, restricting $a_{15}=a_{16}=0$ and $a_{10},a_{11},a_{12} \\geq 0$. Contains 4 HQET (Wilson line) propagators linear in $v.k_i$ and 7 standard massless quadratic propagators. Together with topology 5 and topologies 1-3 from arXiv:1708.01221, accounts for 46 master integrals for all $n_f$-dependent color structures. Three new MIs from topologies 4 and 5 are computed via Feynman parametrization and HyperInt, checked with FIESTA4.",
